      "x": 80, "y": 360,
      "width": 700, "height": 24,
      "text": "Each Q tile loads ONCE from HBM, then iterates ALL KV tiles.",
      "originalText": "Each Q tile loads ONCE from HBM, then iterates ALL KV tiles.",
